title: ClancyEntry
---
<<if !$fabricatorClancyGreeted>>
    <<set $fabricatorClancyGreeted = true>>
    <<jump ClancyIntro>>
<<elseif $scanQuestGiven == false>>
    <<jump ClancyReiterate>>
<<elseif $scanQuestGiven == true>>
    <<jump FollowUpOnScanQuest>>
<<elseif $scanQuestOffered == true>>
    <<jump AskAboutScanQuest>>
<<else>>
    <<jump ClancyGeneral>>
<<endif>>
===

title: ClancyIntro
---

Clancy: How do you do? What brings you to this outpost?

<<greet DialogueCommands FabricatorClancy>>
// <<play_greet_sound DialogueCommands FabricatorClancy>>
-> I'm looking for someone. Someone who might have been a frequent visitor around here 4, 5 years ago.

Clancy: If you have their PI marker, I can run it against our long term logs.
<<smalltalk DialogueCommands FabricatorClancy>>
-> Sure, here you go.. <Give Clancy Access>
    <<jump IKnewHer001>>
// -> I don't know...
// <<jump End02>>
// Unreachable

