Clancy: How can I help you?
-> Nothing for now.
===

title: IKnewHer001
---
Clancy: Yes... I remember your sister. 
Clancy: Ran that outpost to the west. 
Clancy: Place had decent noodles and believable Earth beer.
-> Do you know anything about her dissapearance?
Clancy: No, I don't unfortunately. You might talk to Dr. Hypolita up at the tower.
Clancy: Thing is, she doesn't really agree to meet with strangers. 
Clancy: She does have this job that needs doing and I've been too busy.
Clancy: Will you help us out? I'm sure she will talk to you if you do.
<<smalltalk DialogueCommands FabricatorClancy>>
Clancy: We need some samples taken from the life-forms in the mine across the canyon.
Clancy: It's routine, but they always want me to go in. They study the organisms in the former mine.
-> Sure, I'll go in and do those samplings. Sounds simple enough.
    <<jump AcceptScanQuest>>
===

title: AskAboutScanQuest
---
Clancy: Change your mind on that sampling job in the mine?
-> Yeah, I'll do it.
    <<jump AcceptScanQuest>>
-> I still don't know.
    Clancy: I get it. No pressure.
        <<jump End02>>
===

title: AcceptScanQuest
---
Clancy: Great, heres the sampling tool we use for these types of jobs.
Clancy: It's easy to use. Just point at the clearly liquid filled structures.
<<complete_objective DialogueCommands "TalkToClancy">>
<<give_player_item DialogueCommands "BasicLiquidTool" 1>>
Clancy: It's not dangerous if you're careful. I appreciate your help.
<<add_objective DialogueCommands "GoToScienceMine">>
// <<give_player_keyaccess DialogueCommands "ScienceMineDoorKey">>
<<"mark_poi_as_having_new_content" DialogueCommands "d8d892a8-829f-4f24-a1c4-740cf2df7f6a">>

<<set $scanQuestGiven = true>>
<<jump End02>>
===

title: FollowUpOnScanQuest
---
Clancy: How is it going with those samples?
-> I haven't gotten to it.
    <<jump End02>>
<<if $samplesTaken >= 10>>
-> I got them.
<<endif>>
===

title: ReturnedToClancy
---
Clancy: Well hello, I am glad you made it back safely.
<<pleased DialogueCommands FabricatorClancy>>
<<complete_objective DialogueCommands "ReturnToClancy">>
Clancy: I'll take those samples off your hands. 
<<give_liquid_samples DialogueCommands -1>>
Clancy: I'm sure Dr. Hypolita will do all she can for you after your help.
Clancy: I'll let her know to expect you.
<<add_objective DialogueCommands "SpeakWithHypolita000">>
<<activate_objective DialogueCommands "SpeakWithHypolita000">>

